# Security Checklist — <%= appName %>

Use this checklist alongside automated compliance checks.

## Access control

- [ ] MFA enabled for privileged accounts
- [ ] Least-privilege roles reviewed quarterly
- [ ] Offboarding revokes access within 24 hours

## Change management

- [ ] Production changes require review
- [ ] Deployments are logged and attributable
- [ ] Rollback plan documented

## Monitoring

- [ ] Error and security alerts configured
- [ ] Audit logs retained per policy
- [ ] Incident response runbook tested

## Data protection

- [ ] Encryption in transit (TLS)
- [ ] Secrets not committed to source control
- [ ] Backups tested for restore
